extendedInfo.description: NOTE: A NEW VERSION OF THIS APP IS NOW AVAILABLE.Due to technical limitations of the Play Store, combined with the fact that the two versions of the app are being merged into a new one, a new store listing needed to be created. Please update to the new version by uninstalling this one and installing the new!Sorry for the inconvenience!--Whether you are actively serving in the military, working with military personnel or just interested in military forces, Global Military Ranks is an invaluable companion. Upgrade to the full paid version and get an awesome quiz mode as well!Browse ranks from numerous countries around the world with more being added. Currently featuring the US, Canada, Brazil, Belgium, UK, Germany, Spain, Norway, Sweden, Finland, Japan, The Netherlands, Egypt and Russia with many more additional countries being implemented depending on demand. Each rank is labeled with its corresponding NATO rank code or other equivalent. All branches and ranks have their associated insignia's as well.Test your knowledge with the fully customizable quiz mode and see how many points you can get. What better way to learn the ranks you need to know?Enjoy a large collection of military quotes, motto's and sayings from around the world, beautifully presented every time you start the app.All the above is packed in a stunningly stylish and good looking graphical interface.Global Military Ranks has been designed to work on all versions of Android from 4.0 and up, including Android 4.2. Work is being done on tablet specific designs as well.New ranks and countries will be added soon, and user demand will dictate which countries get added first, so do shout out which ones you want the most.The lone developer has spent countless hours on the data gathering and application development. Purchasing this app will ensure continued development and updates.Full list of currently featured ranks.United States:* Air Force* Army* Coast Guard* Marine Corps* NavyNote: Currently only featuring officer ranks for Navy and Coast Guard.Brazil:* ArmyBelgium:* ArmyCanada* Army* Navy* Air ForceUnited Kingdom:* Air Force* Army* NavyJapan:*ArmySpain:* ArmyRussia:* ArmyNorway:* Army* Air Force* NavySweden:* ArmyGermany* ArmyThe Netherlands* ArmyFinland* ArmyGlobal Military Ranks requests two permissions. Their use is explained below:* WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE: This is necessary in order to store the database on the external storage on the device.* INTERNET: An active internet connection is required in order to download the database.

Grades all screwed up like the OR grades rather than E for enlisted an no such enlisted grade above E-9 in any branch, no such thing as E-10 or E-11 in USMC. Your British Army ranks are all screwed up past Lt. Col. I could go on...CHECK YOUR FACTS AND TRY AGAIN
